{"tid":1376043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 市民請留意警方公布的消息","createTime":"2019-07-28T08:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:04:09.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2edcf69841b1055aee5c8c04e0c36e74953bdd05","tid":1376043,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"市民請留意警方公布的消息<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n  <br />\n  今日（七月二十八日）下午三時，於中環遮打花園有一個公眾集會，部分參與人士在集會開始後約半小時，突然離開集會地點，並走出馬路，沿金鐘道及軒尼詩道，前往灣仔方向。警方預料會對灣仔及銅鑼灣一帶的交通造成影響，請附近的市民注意，並留意警方公布的消息。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月28日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間16時16分"},{"pid":"cb9d840b6154274af227be146ec14cc11ddab0d6","tid":1376043,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/28/P2019072800610.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F28%2FP2019072800610.htm&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3whAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=541dbbbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/28/P2019072800610.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cdb34b79601a3b9c22349a5b8bf9461a761e17f7","tid":1376043,"uid":98431,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"形式上大家開始做到如水<br />\n<br />\n麻煩思想上都準備一下 「人心不撤 不等於人身不撤」<br />\n<br />\n廢事又俾人話係鬼 分化前線<br />\n<br />\n睇路阿屌 依家興玩黑白配"},{"pid":"c47c51015f9d5089760d50024ad4ba4d0dc4e577","tid":1376043,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:29:26.000Z","msg":"殺班警犬一個措手不及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2264558fe2dda95a6354149d54c0edfcf15990","tid":1376043,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"交通消息?"},{"pid":"23950bfe63e0054f0f4e955e4b